    "title": "The Past: passé composé",
    "explanation": "Paul a fermé la porte. Avant, il a chargé la fusée. — notice the pattern: a + [verb with -é]. This describes a completed past action.\n\nThe formula is avoir + past participle: a fermé (closed), a chargé (loaded), a changé (changed).\n\nRe-read and find every a + [past verb]. What happened before the current scene?"
